=== PRE-REQUISITE:
    Swarm clustor has to be setup as explained in Lesson-4

=== Multi-container application on multi-host cluster

    1)  Login to manager1                                   docker-machine ssh manager1
    2)  Create a new yaml file as similar like Lesson-5
    3)  Deploy application to Swarm:                        docker stack deploy --compose-file=docker-compose.yml [service name]
    4)  Check the deployment:                               docker stack ls
                                                            docker service ls
    5)  Remove stack:                                       docker stack rm [service_name]

